- Verify the generated `courseId` is active, published, and exists in the system.
- If the AI generates an invalid or deleted `courseId`, sanitize the resource (change type to `"article"` or `"video"` and remove `courseId`) to avoid broken links.

### Phase 6 & 7: Frontend Course Recommendation UI
